This license protects ValiNum innovation while encouraging community collaboration.

1. Personal and Educational Use
The use of compiled ValiNum versions (distributed via NPM  or CDN) is entirely free, including within a company for commercial projects. You may use the library to validate numbers in your applications without any payment to FomaDev.

2. Contributions (Fork & Pull Request)
Forks are authorized ONLY for contributing to the official FomaDev project. Any improvements must be submitted via a Pull Request to the original repository. By contributing, you agree that your code will be integrated under this same license.

3. Commercial Use and Competition (PAID)
A paid commercial license is MANDATORY for the following cases:
- Selling or distributing a modified version of the source code as a standalone product.
- Integrating ValiNum source code directly into another commercial library or framework intended for sale.
- Creating a paid API or Cloud service based specifically on the ValiNum validation engine.
- Developing derivative validation products based on this specific logic and codebase.

4. Prohibition of Independent Forks
Maintaining a separate version (permanent Fork) of this project to bypass FomaDev's authority or to create a competing library is strictly prohibited.

5. Licensing Contact
To obtain commercial authorization or negotiate an exploitation license, contact Fordi (FomaDev) directly.
